## ğŸš€ Features

* ğŸ”„ **Real-time** bi-directional messaging via Socket.IO
* ğŸŒ **ASGI** server built on FastAPI + Uvicorn
* ğŸ›¡ï¸ **JWT Authentication** (or pluggable auth middleware)
* ğŸ”§ **Tool Presets** for `translate_text`, `summarize_text`, `generate_code` calls
* ğŸ”„ **WebSocket Bridge** to Gemini (`models/gemini-2.0-flash-exp`)
* ğŸ“Š **Optional Metrics** (active connections, processed messages, errors)
* ğŸ›¬ **Graceful Startup & Shutdown**
* ğŸ”§  **Configurable** : CORS, retry/backoff, hooks, debug logging

