## ğŸ’¡ Examples

### Translate Text

```js
socket.emit('message', {
  toolCall: {
    functionName: 'translate_text',
    arguments: { text: 'Hello, world!', targetLanguage: 'es' }
  }
});
```

### Summarize Text

```js
socket.emit('message', {
  toolCall: {
    functionName: 'summarize_text',
    arguments: { text: longParagraph, maxLength: 50 }
  }
});
```

